EntryRemoved(bytes32,bytes4).details: Emitted when an entry is removed.

params.sig: The signature of the method the entry is describing.

EntryUpserted(bytes32,bytes4,address,byt.details: Emitted when an entry is inserted or updated.

params.cid: The IPFS CID of the file containing the Radspec description.
params.sig: The signature of the method the entry is describing.
params.submitter: The address that upserted the entry.

getEntry(bytes32,bytes4).details: Get an entry from the registry.

params._sig: The signature of the method the entry is describing.

returns._0: The CID, submitter, and status of the entry.

params._scopes: The list of contract's bytecode hash.

removeEntry(bytes32,bytes4).details: Remove an entry from the registry.

params._sig: The signature of the method the entry is describing.

params._cids: The list of IPFS CIDs of the file containing the description.
params._scopes: The list of contract's bytecode hash.

params._cid: The IPFS CID of the file containing the description.
params._sig: The signature of the method the entry is describing.
